{"tid":2379060,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴西空難 足球隊5人亡","createTime":"2021-01-25T03:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T00:52:27.000Z","uid":57035,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7b7d3278c1a3c45d99b569c99fa307ebb99d6f43","tid":2379060,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:42:51.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】巴西第4級別聯賽地區足球隊帕爾馬斯（Palmas）的主席和4名球員，昨日搭乘小型飛前往參賽時不幸遇上空難死亡。路透社報道，該小型飛機在帕爾馬斯市一個小型機場起飛，原定飛往大約800公里外的戈亞尼亞（Goiania）參與周一賽事，但飛機起飛不久即撞落跑道尾段，5名死者包括球隊主席梅拉（Lucas Meira）、以及4名球員普拉克西德斯（Lucas Praxedes）、諾爾（Guilherme Noe）、拉努利（Ranule）及莫利納里（Marcus Molinari）。飛機的機師亦死亡；飛機型號昨日未見披露。<br />\n<br />\n（路透社）"},{"pid":"3f983c45860bd3531d1121213cd58cfc5e9b6f4b","tid":2379060,"uid":363990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:46:53.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"4fb86c5c0c3328cb2c8d1383013fdf0fd75f81cd","tid":2379060,"uid":282744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:47:12.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d2ea3eda6a3807bec6ea16dc50622d134462f9","tid":2379060,"uid":34899,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:50:41.000Z","msg":"又係巴西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nrip"},{"pid":"5d37a55d4435ee2af59740bcd08dfd10f11544eb","tid":2379060,"uid":202348,"like":15,"dislike":7,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:54:54.000Z","msg":"利狗x錯人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ff80e47bbcb1c19274295c66dfc332660bba2b","tid":2379060,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:05:04.000Z","msg":"今年都係多災難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n月頭又有單空難"},{"pid":"beba7f9355a3706daf4c19ce3acb3275eba3dfc2","tid":2379060,"uid":44285,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:09:41.000Z","msg":"利狗輸波姐，唔使搞到人空難㗎"},{"pid":"0e5a3a27380a0